original_title: Beautiful Fish of the Kelp Forest
overview: A group of lucky children journeys beneath the sea for an up-close and personal look at a majestic kelp forest, full of a ton of wondrous and fascinating sea critters including garibaldi fish, eels, starfish, lobsters and more. As we view these remarkable underwater creatures in their natural habitats, experts explain the ins and outs of this delicate and beautiful ecosystem and reveal how these diverse species sustain life.
title: Beautiful Fish of the Kelp Forest
